headline: A competitive market environment continues: Aon's Fall 2025 Canadian Insurance Market Update
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, has released its Fall 2025 Canadian Insurance Market Update. Published in support of Aon's ongoing commitment to help Canadian clients make better decisions about risk management and insurance programs, the report finds that the Canadian Property and Casualty (P&C) market is characterized by soft conditions marked by increased capacity, strong underwriting performance and heightened competition.
